Bug ID:008 
Title: 8. After clicking the "Next" or "Prev" buttons they still glow.
Description: After going to the Reservation page and clicking the "Next" or "Prev" buttons they still glow.

Steps to Reproduce:
Step 1: Open browser and go to (https://lzcbvwog.acmebooking.com/).
Step 2: Log into your account.
Step 3: Click on Reservations in the navbar.
Step 5: Click the Next or Prev buttons.
Step 6: Affirm that they remain glowing after being clicked.

Expected Result:
After clicking the "Next" or "Prev" buttons they should glow in the moment of clicking but not after that.
Actual Result:
After clicking the "Next" or "Prev" buttons they remain glowing.

Severity:
Low  

Priority:
Low

Additional Information:
-

Environment:
Browser: Brave 1.70.119, Mozilla Firefox 130.0.1 (64-bit)
Operating System: Windows 10, Windows 11
Device: Desktop PC
Network:Ethernet
